items.title: BlackRock Large Cap Focus Growth V.I. Fund Q4 2024 Commentary
items.description: The fund posted a return of 6.12% (Class I shares) for the fourth quarter of 2024. The largest exposures were in the IT, consumer discretionary, and communication services sectors.
